object.text: Press Esc key or Start button to continue

object.name: instruction
object.text:
Using the Xbox controller or keyboard:
Move Jenny with the D-Pad, Left Stick, or arrow keys.

object.name: instruction
object.text: Press and hold the A button or Z key to fire Jenny's sting weapon at invading insects.

object.name: instruction
object.text: Press the B button or X key to change the weapon type.

object.name: instruction
object.text: Press the X button or C key to switch between slow and fast movement speed.

object.name: instruction
object.text:
Shoot Honey Pots to release precious Honey Crystals.
When Jenny touches a Crystal, she gains a weapon level and a moment of invincibility.

object.name: instruction
object.text:
If Jenny is hit by a bullet or enemy flying at her height, she loses a weapon level.
If Jenny has no more weapon levels, she loses a life.

object.name: instruction
object.text: Score enough points and Jenny will earn an extra life!

object.name: instruction
object.text:
You win if Jenny defeats the boss insects before the timer runs out.
You lose if Jenny's lives or timer run out.
